  "texts": [
    "A cork borer was used to punch out leaf discs surrounding the necrotic lesion area 48 h postPBS 1 = T 12 + T 13 -T 23 2,inoculation, or, for the controls, leaf discs surrounding the agar plug.",
    "Leaf discs were then put into 2-mL cryovial tubes and flash frozen using liquid nitrogen.",
    "RNA was extracted according to the protocol outlined in the previous section.",
    "Library construction and sequencing were done at The Pennsylvania State University Huck Institutes of the Life Sciences Genomics Core Facility.",
    "Stranded, single end, 150 nt libraries were sequenced on two high output runs of an Illumina Next-Seq 550."
  ],
